Package nusri.fyp.demo.state_machine

Class Node

java.lang.Object
nusri.fyp.demo.state_machine.Node
public class Node extends Object
Represents a node in a state machine process.
This class handles the management of a node's actions, probabilities, and quotas, as well as interactions with parent nodes.

  • Field Details

    • name

      private final String name
      The name of the node.

    • id

      private final int id
      The unique identifier of the node.

    • visitProbability

      private double visitProbability
      The probability of visiting the node.
      This represents how likely the node is to be traversed in the state machine.

    • realQuota

      private final double realQuota
      The real quota associated with the node.
      This represents the actual workload capacity or limit of the node.

    • probability

      private double probability
      The current probability value (P(N)) for the node.
      This represents the probability of the node being selected or processed in the state machine.

    • parents

      private final Set<Node> parents
      A set of parent nodes for the current node.
      These represent the nodes that must be processed before this node can be activated.

    • actions

      private final List<String> actions
      A list of actions associated with the node.
      These actions define what operations or transitions are linked to the node.

    • firstAllocation

      Map<String,Double> firstAllocation
      A map holding the first allocation probabilities for various actions.
      This represents the initial probabilities assigned to different actions for the node.
